code: @Override public Object postProcessBeforeInitialization(Object bean, String beanName) throws BeansException {     if (this.bootstrapContext != null && bean instanceof BootstrapContextAware) {         ((BootstrapContextAware) bean).setBootstrapContext(this.bootstrapContext).     }     return bean. }
@Override public Object postProcessAfterInitialization(Object bean, String beanName) throws BeansException {     return bean. }
